  <name>OpenAnime</name>
  <summary>Unofficial Linux desktop client for OpenAnime</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OpenAnime is an unofficial desktop client for OpenAnime, specifically optimized for Linux. It features hardware acceleration for smooth 4K playback.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><em>Hardware Acceleration:</em> Smooth 4K playback powered by WebGPU and Vulkan compatibility.</li>
      <li><em>Frameless UI:</em> Custom window controls that auto-hide for an immersive viewing experience.</li>
      <li><em>Linux Optimized:</em> specifically tuned for minimal resource usage and maximum performance on Linux desktops.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
